---
title: Japanese Yuzu Miso-Glazed Trout with Cucumber Carrot Salad
description: For Asian Heritage Month, we bring you this traditional meal that celebrates the flavors and presentation we love about Japanese cuisine, all highlighted by a savory, citrusy yuzu-miso glaze from women-owned Asian sauce company Omsom. Top a mound of fluffy rice with flaky, miso-glazed roasted trout and serve alongside a tangy, crisp sesame cucumber and carrot salad for fresh, crunchy contrast.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/661d65723d20ae432f30b536-8a7a3bfb.jpeg
